---
title: "Data Visualization"
---

- presenting complex information in a graphical format that is easy to interpret
	- critical in **transforming raw data into meaningful insights**
- data can be summarized effectively to provide actionable insights through various methods
	- counts
	- totals
	- averages
	- trends
- Helps businesses in
	- optimize operations
	- track Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)
	- forecast future trends
